Package serverSide.entities

Class PlaygroundClientProxy

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Thread
      • serverSide.entities.PlaygroundClientProxy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CoachCloning, ContestantCloning, RefereeCloning, java.lang.Runnable
    public class PlaygroundClientProxy
extends java.lang.Thread
implements CoachCloning, ContestantCloning, RefereeCloning
    Service provider agent for access to the Playground. Implementation of a client-server model of type 2 (server replication). Communication is based on a communication channel under the TCP protocol.
